title: Spacious Renovated Top Floor 1 Bed/1 Bath in Noe Valley!
posting_body: ['348 Duncan Street, San Francisco, CA', 'Noe Valley is a community offering a great residential environment, upscale amenities and excellent service for our residents.', 'Our designer put careful thought into custom features such as cedar-lined closets with built-in closet organization systems.', 'The gourmet kitchen boasts a stainless steel appliance package, including an 18-bottle wine refrigerator with digital touch screen controls and temperature display.', 'Granite countertops, custom backsplash, and white cabinetry are the perfect blend of functionality and elegance.', 'You must see this custom home to understand the value of exquisite finishes carved out of a traditional apartment floor plan.', 'We are a pet friendly building!', 'Pet Deposit is $500 and there is a monthly pet rent of $35/month for cats and $50/month for dogs.', '*Some breed restrictions do apply*', 'Safe and easy self -guided tour available.', 'Lease Terms', 'Deposit: $1000', 'Lease duration: 12 months', 'Details', '1 Bed / 1 Bath     in Noe Valley', 'Rent:', '$3,495', '/month', '650 square feet', 'Pets Allowed: Cats & Dogs', 'Amenities', 'Fireplace', 'In Unit Laundry']
